room_title: Escape room "The Time Collector" by Ultimate Escape Game in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description: A crazy scientist and his intrepid grandson have hired you to obtain a one-of-a-kind Portal Gun. This Portal Gun is owned by a man who has affectionately been named “The Time Collector” because of his great love of science fiction memorabilia. You must sneak into The Time Collector’s museum, steal the Portal Gun, and get out within the one hour before he returns to his museum.
